scheduled_maintenances.name: Scheduled Maintenance for the US and EU Region - August 20th

incident_updates.body:
We intend to perform maintenance on Sunday, August 20th from 05:00 to 06:00 UTC (or Saturday, August 19th from 22:00 to 23:00 PT). Customers in the US and EU can expect a short service interruption at some point during this timeframe which may include: 
- issues accessing and loading the New Relic UI
- anomalies for synthetics checks
- timeouts and errors with queries for customers utilizing New Relic for Azure Cloud Monitoring

All further updates will be posted here on our status page.
